work-overlay/
=============
Staging area for Phase 2 — files to be moved into the private work dotfiles repo
(jerry-feng-skydio/dotfiles).

Directory layout after migration:
  ~/.dotfiles-work/
    personal/              ← git submodule: https://github.com/jfeng94/dotfiles
    .bashrc_local          ← work bash config
    .vimrc_local           ← vim-lcm rtp + work skyrg glob-source
    .vimrc_plugins_local   ← djinni/kotlin/swift/AnsiEsc Vundle plugins
    .gitconfig_local       ← work git identity + signing key
    skyrg/
      global_work.vim      ← Device page, watch_usb()
      actions_aircam.vim   ← aircam context actions
      projects_aircam.vim  ← aircam rg filter presets
    setup.sh               ← delegates to personal/setup.sh, then work-specific steps

Migration steps (run in ~/.dotfiles-work):
  git submodule add https://github.com/jfeng94/dotfiles personal
  git rm --cached .bashrc .vimrc .tmux.conf .gitconfig .inputrc coc-settings.json
  rm .bashrc .vimrc .tmux.conf .gitconfig .inputrc coc-settings.json
  # copy files from this directory into repo root
  git add .
  git commit -m "refactor: delegate to personal dotfiles submodule"

After migration, setup is:
  cd ~/.dotfiles-work && bash setup.sh --all

Node version:
  Work setup pins NODE_VERSION=20 (override: NODE_VERSION=22 bash setup.sh --all)
